{"tid":1091583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麻省理工終止與華為中興合作 香港列受審查地區","createTime":"2019-04-04T08:39:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T08:04:49.000Z","uid":5195,"like":90,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d614053eac2cea464ddac94a4c34afc7e06a14d0","tid":1091583,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T08:39:29.000Z","msg":"麻省理工學院（Massachusetts Institute of Technology，MIT）宣布，決定結束與中國電訊設備商華為及中興（00763）的合作關係。學院聲明指出，基於聯邦政府違反制裁的調查，麻省理工學院不再接受與華為、中興或其各自子公司的新合作，以及不更新現有的合作項目。<br />\n<br />\n加強部分國家合作審查審查   香港包括在內<br />\n<br />\n聲明又指，最近決定當與某些國家合作時，目前包括中國、 俄羅斯和沙特阿拉伯，需要額外的學院和行政審查，當中包括香港。MIT此舉顯示其對科研夥伴加強審查。"},{"pid":"57401e3622dc908fa1abe7be7f0bd3ecf9e1c8d5","tid":1091583,"uid":124277,"like":7,"dislike":93,"score":-86,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T08:40:58.000Z","msg":"咁忌才,咁唔大方嘅學校, 唔會有作為"},{"pid":"1f839699239385b6fa97d774ee30b088ad2f31fb","tid":1091583,"uid":144695,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"57401e3622dc908fa1abe7be7f0bd3ecf9e1c8d5","tid":1091583,"uid":124277,"like":7,"dislike":93,"score":-86,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T08:40:58.000Z","msg":"咁忌才,咁唔大方嘅學校, 唔會有作為"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T08:42:59.000Z","msg":"忌才？邊撚到才啊睇過"},{"pid":"e652b2f4cb99f4d3a2e06dbf391bb6d12770dd51","tid":1091583,"uid":174767,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T08:43:24.000Z","msg":"強烈讉責！！！！"},{"pid":"91aa768e2fd99197bb97cdc9e361b7a2bfb2248f","tid":1091583,"uid":124277,"like":2,"dislike":37,"score":-35,"quote":{"pid":"1f839699239385b6fa97d774ee30b088ad2f31fb","tid":1091583,"uid":144695,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"57401e3622dc908fa1abe7be7f0bd3ecf9e1c8d5","tid":1091583,"uid":124277,"like":7,"dislike":93,"score":-86,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T08:40:58.000Z","msg":"咁忌才,咁唔大方嘅學校, 唔會有作為"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T08:42:59.000Z","msg":"忌才？邊撚到才啊睇過"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T08:44:12.000Z","msg":"5g 喎, 你有?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" 